PPT2NCL Version 0.9.0 (alpha)
Welcome to PPT2NCL, the first ppt (Microsoft Power Point format) converter to ncl (Nested Context Language).

What's new in version 0.9.0 (alpha)
=========================================================================
  In this version PPT2NCL can convert PPT presentations in simples NCL presentations. 
  Currently, PPT2NCL uses the HSFL library version 3.1 (http://http://poi.apache.org/slideshow/index.html).
This library supports the following types of pictures:
    * Windows Metafiles (WMF)
    * Enhanced Metafiles (EMF)
    * JPEG Interchange Format
    * Portable Network Graphics (PNG)
    * Macintosh PICT

  In current version PPT2NCL is not able to work with animations and transitions
from ppt format and can not understand the PPTX format.
This features will be supported in the future.

Release History
=========================================================================
Version 0.9.0 is the first PPT2NCL release.

Download the lastest version
=========================================================================
You can download the latest version of PPT2NCL at http://www.ncl.org.br

Download the source code
=========================================================================
PPT2NCL is a free software and its source code is available at 
http://www.softwarepublico.gov.br (Portal do Software Publico Brasileiro).

